org.stormdev.mc.servermonitor.api.reports

Interface CombinedLagReport

  • All Superinterfaces:
    LagReport, ServerEventReport

    public interface CombinedLagReport
extends LagReport
    Represents the default lag report generated when TPS is below threshold or memory is above threshold
